Definition: a congenital disorder caused by having an extra 21st chromosome
Example: results in a flat face and short stature and mental retardation
Synonyms: mongolianism, Down, s_syndrome, Down_syndrome, trisomy_, trisomy, birth_defect, a, congenital, disorder, caused, by, having, an, extra, st, chromosome, results, in, flat, face, and, short, stature, mental, retardation
Category: noun.state
